pages.body:
Zozon notes:

Very nice clean design.

Help shall open in new tab/window not to destroy existing authoring

Things wish I have:
* name spaces (page list is flat)
* timed signature (making notes dated easily)
* cloning to my wiki and interwiki links

Nice parts:
* cannot create page if not logged in (+)
* mobie friendly - responsive design (bootstrap?) (++)

Cloning trial notes:
* http://127.0.0.1:43110/1gJAQS5M8TdFvmBPoJZccPohLmn6LDRY1/
* http://127.0.0.1:43110/1NTwqW1vkwCHpGf8eS7XKKp5yDhjExY1eF/?Page:home

20/3/2016 not really clear how to clone - presence of files of unknown purpose...

cloning was  done simply but function is missing.
